*This website documents the public API for Uiza version 4.0*

The Uiza APIs are HTTP-based [RESTful](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Representational_State_Transfer) APIs. Our API has predictable, resource-oriented URLs, accepts [form-encoded](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/POST_(HTTP)#Use_for_submitting_web_forms) request bodies, returns [JSON-encoded](https://www.json.org) responses, and uses HTTP response codes, authentication, verbs.

```Important: You cannot run the sample requests in this guide as-is. Replace call-specific parameters such as tokens and AppIDs with your own values.```

